1. *Publika* je bila oduševljena predstavom. (The audience was thrilled with the performance.)
2. Organizator je očekivao veliku *publiku* na koncertu. (The organizer expected a large audience at the concert.)
3. Glavni cilj televizijske kuće je da privuče što veću *publiku*. (The main goal of the television station is to attract a larger audience.)
4. *Publika* je burno reagovala na politički govor. (The audience reacted strongly to the political speech.)
5. Ova knjiga je namenjena širokoj *publici*. (This book is intended for a wide audience.)
6. Pozorište će organizovati besplatan program za *publiku*. (The theater will organize a free program for the audience.)
7. Umetnik je uvek želeo da izazove reakciju kod *publike*. (The artist always wanted to provoke a reaction from the audience.)
8. Na konferenciji će biti prisutna *publika* iz celog sveta. (The conference will be attended by an audience from all over the world.)
9. *Publika* je pljeskala nakon završetka predstave. (The audience applauded at the end of the performance.)
10. Ovaj film je privukao veliku *publiku* u bioskopima. (This film attracted a large audience in cinemas.)